WEBVTT

00:00:14.760 --> 00:00:15.360 line:80%
Master.

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:18.960 line:80%
There's some progress on another matter.

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:21.720 line:80%
If the Marquis of Wu'an

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:23.310 line:80%
truly is alive,

00:00:23.870 --> 00:00:24.870 line:80%
what should we do?

00:00:31.560 --> 00:00:34.120 line:80%
That will be a blessing for Great Yin.

00:00:37.270 --> 00:00:39.470 line:80%
There are palace intrigues up ahead

00:00:40.040 --> 00:00:43.080 line:80%
and Prince Changxin's rebellion
looming behind.

00:00:43.640 --> 00:00:47.830 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an
is a pillar of stability.

00:02:18.240 --> 00:02:23.410 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:02:23.490 --> 00:02:26.020 line:80%
[Episode 10]

00:03:03.320 --> 00:03:04.080 line:80%
Father,

00:03:04.390 --> 00:03:05.230 line:80%
Mother.

00:03:10.110 --> 00:03:10.880 line:80%
Don't cry.

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:18.800 line:80%
Master, who is buried
behind this nameless stele?

00:03:24.600 --> 00:03:26.280 line:80%
Today is Father's birthday.

00:03:27.580 --> 00:03:28.910 line:80%
Let's be happy.

00:03:29.640 --> 00:03:31.670 line:80%
That way,
Father and Mother can be at peace

00:03:31.670 --> 00:03:33.070 line:80%
watching us from heaven.

00:03:44.320 --> 00:03:47.040 line:80%
Fan Erniu. Meng Lihua.

00:03:49.360 --> 00:03:50.160 line:80%
Fan...

00:03:51.640 --> 00:03:54.100 line:80%
Could they have been
using another surname?

00:03:55.550 --> 00:03:58.600 line:80%
The current situation is complicated.

00:03:59.390 --> 00:04:01.990 line:80%
So much helplessness lies beneath.

00:04:02.600 --> 00:04:04.200 line:80%
When the time is right,

00:04:04.390 --> 00:04:06.550 line:80%
I will tell you everything.

00:04:10.390 --> 00:04:11.670 line:80%
It's been 16 years.

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:16.449 line:80%
It's time for the truth to come to light.

00:04:17.370 --> 00:04:19.590 line:80%
Zheng, burn the paper money.

00:04:25.240 --> 00:04:27.200 line:80%
There's still some paper money at home.

00:04:27.200 --> 00:04:29.860 line:80%
When we get back,
burn some for your parents too.

00:04:33.459 --> 00:04:35.120 line:80%
Does burning these things...

00:04:35.730 --> 00:04:36.870 line:80%
really work?

00:04:40.780 --> 00:04:41.630 line:80%
Of course.

00:04:43.550 --> 00:04:45.880 line:80%
People burn paper money during festivals

00:04:46.680 --> 00:04:48.610 line:80%
to tell their deceased loved ones

00:04:52.100 --> 00:04:53.700 line:80%
that we still remember them.

00:04:54.400 --> 00:04:55.070 line:80%
Wenkan,

00:04:55.580 --> 00:04:57.370 line:80%
promise me one thing.

00:04:58.040 --> 00:05:00.980 line:80%
If one day I'm gone,

00:05:01.190 --> 00:05:03.280 line:80%
you must take good care of

00:05:03.280 --> 00:05:04.740 line:80%
the two Fan sisters for me.

00:05:04.870 --> 00:05:07.250 line:80%
Never let them get involved.

00:05:07.270 --> 00:05:09.100 line:80%
Master, you are in such good health.

00:05:09.100 --> 00:05:10.230 line:80%
Why say such things?

00:05:12.750 --> 00:05:14.070 line:80%
That day will come.

00:05:15.110 --> 00:05:15.800 line:80%
Promise me.

00:05:19.850 --> 00:05:20.810 line:80%
I promise you.

00:05:26.650 --> 00:05:27.860 line:80%
Don't burn so much.

00:05:41.480 --> 00:05:42.140 line:80%
Don't move.

00:05:43.430 --> 00:05:45.630 line:80%
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

00:05:46.700 --> 00:05:47.900 line:80%
♪ With very pale colors ♪

00:05:48.700 --> 00:05:51.660 line:80%
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

00:05:52.120 --> 00:05:54.610 line:80%
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

00:05:55.360 --> 00:05:56.690 line:80%
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

00:05:57.520 --> 00:06:01.680 line:80%
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

00:06:00.880 --> 00:06:04.430 line:80%
You two look just like Father and Mother.

00:06:10.520 --> 00:06:11.610 line:80%
Thanks.

00:06:13.320 --> 00:06:14.250 line:80%
You're welcome.

00:06:24.670 --> 00:06:25.670 line:80%
Come, Changning.

00:06:42.160 --> 00:06:43.820 line:80%
What's wrong with your wrist?

00:06:43.910 --> 00:06:47.310 line:80%
The ox cart tipped over
when I was collecting pigs yesterday.

00:06:47.430 --> 00:06:49.030 line:80%
I used my hand to break the fall

00:06:49.030 --> 00:06:49.920 line:80%
and sprained it.

00:06:49.920 --> 00:06:52.030 line:80%
Changyu's wrist hurts often.

00:06:52.060 --> 00:06:54.110 line:80%
Butchering pigs is tiring work.

00:06:58.990 --> 00:07:01.690 line:80%
Constant strain on the wrist
over the years can lead to tendon pain.

00:07:01.690 --> 00:07:03.550 line:80%
Luckily the bone isn't affected.

00:07:04.760 --> 00:07:07.370 line:80%
But you need to be careful from now on.

00:07:11.020 --> 00:07:12.160 line:80%
On the way back later,

00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:14.640 line:80%
I'll get off at the grocery store
to buy something.

00:07:14.640 --> 00:07:16.130 line:80%
You don't have money, right? Here.

00:07:16.130 --> 00:07:17.260 line:80%
No need. I have some.

00:07:18.070 --> 00:07:19.470 line:80%
How would you have money?

00:07:21.980 --> 00:07:23.180 line:80%
Get in the cart first.

00:07:26.820 --> 00:07:28.960 line:80%
Then you two go home first
after I'm done shopping.

00:07:28.960 --> 00:07:31.290 line:80%
I'll go buy you some tangerine peel candy.

00:07:31.290 --> 00:07:31.840 line:80%
Okay.

00:07:32.810 --> 00:07:34.300 line:80%
Changyu is the best.

00:07:45.430 --> 00:07:45.959 line:80%
You...

00:07:46.950 --> 00:07:48.400 line:80%
People keep dying

00:07:48.400 --> 00:07:49.920 line:80%
in Xigu Lane.

00:07:49.920 --> 00:07:51.070 line:80%
Maybe we've provoked

00:07:51.070 --> 00:07:51.959 line:80%
some kind of spirit.

00:07:51.959 --> 00:07:52.990 line:80%
It's bad luck.

00:07:52.990 --> 00:07:53.670 line:80%
Exactly.

00:07:53.670 --> 00:07:56.230 line:80%
It seems this rice water isn't enough.

00:07:56.840 --> 00:07:57.550 line:80%
In a moment,

00:07:57.550 --> 00:07:59.610 line:80%
I need to find some dry mugwort leaves

00:08:00.550 --> 00:08:02.670 line:80%
and hang them on this door.

00:08:02.870 --> 00:08:03.960 line:80%
Exactly.

00:08:07.530 --> 00:08:09.330 line:80%
Look at that jinx.

00:08:09.460 --> 00:08:10.400 line:80%
Exactly.

00:08:10.400 --> 00:08:12.130 line:80%
She was actually staring at us.

00:08:15.480 --> 00:08:16.430 line:80%
You're back?

00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:21.720 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:08:23.460 --> 00:08:24.750 line:80%
You look listless.

00:08:27.070 --> 00:08:28.230 line:80%
Why are you all wet?

00:08:29.070 --> 00:08:31.530 line:80%
The snow was deep.
It must have been the snow.

00:08:36.800 --> 00:08:37.520 line:80%
Wait.

00:08:43.310 --> 00:08:44.310 line:80%
Was someone bullying you

00:08:44.310 --> 00:08:46.110 line:80%
and saying bad things about you?

00:08:46.150 --> 00:08:48.100 line:80%
Who dares to do that?

00:08:48.550 --> 00:08:50.010 line:80%
I'd knock their teeth out.

00:08:50.830 --> 00:08:52.560 line:80%
I'm going to change my clothes.

00:08:56.430 --> 00:08:59.680 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:09:03.920 --> 00:09:04.760 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:09:05.350 --> 00:09:06.240 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:09:06.550 --> 00:09:08.190 line:80%
Come out here! Fan Changyu!

00:09:09.310 --> 00:09:10.760 line:80%
Fan Changyu! You...

00:09:12.640 --> 00:09:13.370 line:80%
Fan Changyu,

00:09:13.800 --> 00:09:15.090 line:80%
your sister pushed our Hutou

00:09:15.090 --> 00:09:16.850 line:80%
down the stairs at noon.

00:09:17.160 --> 00:09:17.880 line:80%
Look.

00:09:18.400 --> 00:09:20.190 line:80%
He lost two front teeth.

00:09:20.190 --> 00:09:21.800 line:80%
Tell me,
what are you going to do about it?

00:09:21.800 --> 00:09:23.530 line:80%
My sister has always been weak.

00:09:23.650 --> 00:09:26.180 line:80%
Your grandson is years older than her.

00:09:27.070 --> 00:09:28.870 line:80%
How could she possibly push him?

00:09:28.950 --> 00:09:29.350 line:80%
Well...

00:09:29.350 --> 00:09:31.000 line:80%
Granny Kang, let's talk this over calmly.

00:09:31.000 --> 00:09:33.660 line:80%
You're making a scene
in front of the neighbors.

00:09:34.400 --> 00:09:36.000 line:80%
The Fan family bullied my grandson.

00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:38.310 line:80%
Why should I be afraid of
being laughed at?

00:09:38.310 --> 00:09:39.190 line:80%
Isn't it normal for kids to have

00:09:39.190 --> 00:09:41.120 line:80%
a few bumps and scrapes
when they're playing around?

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:42.260 line:80%
-Stop shouting.
-Whether you have the right

00:09:42.260 --> 00:09:43.920 line:80%
to demand justice here or not,

00:09:44.070 --> 00:09:46.000 line:80%
we need to ask Fan Changning first.

00:09:46.950 --> 00:09:48.670 line:80%
Changning, come out.

00:09:52.920 --> 00:09:54.050 line:80%
Come out. It's okay.

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:56.470 line:80%
Changning, come here.

00:09:57.950 --> 00:09:58.520 line:80%
Come.

00:10:00.070 --> 00:10:01.830 line:80%
Changyu wants to ask you something.

00:10:01.830 --> 00:10:02.550 line:80%
Come here.

00:10:04.400 --> 00:10:05.120 line:80%
Come.

00:10:06.040 --> 00:10:06.880 line:80%
Let me ask you.

00:10:08.190 --> 00:10:09.250 line:80%
Did you push Hutou?

00:10:12.400 --> 00:10:13.280 line:80%
Look at that.

00:10:13.280 --> 00:10:15.160 line:80%
Such a little child
already knows how to lie.

00:10:15.160 --> 00:10:16.280 line:80%
She nodded just now,

00:10:16.280 --> 00:10:18.010 line:80%
and now she's shaking her head.

00:10:18.800 --> 00:10:20.530 line:80%
Fan Changning, I'm asking you.

00:10:20.550 --> 00:10:21.640 line:80%
Don't lie.

00:10:21.640 --> 00:10:22.710 line:80%
Lying will make your mouth rot.

00:10:22.710 --> 00:10:23.040 line:80%
You know that?

00:10:23.040 --> 00:10:23.670 line:80%
Get away!

00:10:27.550 --> 00:10:29.550 line:80%
How dare you push me!

00:10:30.120 --> 00:10:32.280 line:80%
Is there no justice left?

00:10:32.670 --> 00:10:35.400 line:80%
The Fan family is so arrogant!

00:10:36.880 --> 00:10:39.000 line:80%
They made my grandson like this,

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:41.550 line:80%
and... and she's acting
as if she's completely in the right!

00:10:41.550 --> 00:10:42.350 line:80%
Stop shouting!

00:10:42.350 --> 00:10:43.040 line:80%
Alright.

00:10:43.640 --> 00:10:44.670 line:80%
See if I will shove your head

00:10:44.670 --> 00:10:45.930 line:80%
into the swill bucket!

00:10:46.550 --> 00:10:47.760 line:80%
I held back earlier

00:10:48.760 --> 00:10:49.830 line:80%
because I didn't know

00:10:49.830 --> 00:10:51.290 line:80%
who my family had offended

00:10:51.350 --> 00:10:53.040 line:80%
to bring trouble to Xigu Lane.

00:10:53.350 --> 00:10:55.410 line:80%
I feel guilty towards the neighbors,

00:10:55.520 --> 00:10:56.980 line:80%
but I haven't wronged you.

00:10:57.640 --> 00:11:00.360 line:80%
People keep dying in your family
these days.

00:11:00.590 --> 00:11:03.470 line:80%
Everyone in the lane knows
that you jinxed them!

00:11:03.470 --> 00:11:05.920 line:80%
You and Mrs. Song
gossip about me every day.

00:11:06.400 --> 00:11:07.800 line:80%
Do you think I don't know?

00:11:08.830 --> 00:11:09.350 line:80%
Fine.

00:11:13.550 --> 00:11:15.200 line:80%
I'll grant your wish today.

00:11:16.830 --> 00:11:17.890 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:11:19.040 --> 00:11:20.890 line:80%
The neighbors are watching.

00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:22.760 line:80%
Do you dare commit violence here?

00:11:22.760 --> 00:11:25.310 line:80%
You've already ruined my reputation.

00:11:26.140 --> 00:11:27.430 line:80%
You don't think I still care

00:11:27.430 --> 00:11:28.760 line:80%
what they think, do you?

00:11:30.670 --> 00:11:32.400 line:80%
If I really do something to you,

00:11:33.420 --> 00:11:35.080 line:80%
do you think they'll help you?

00:11:42.830 --> 00:11:43.490 line:80%
Changning.

00:11:45.760 --> 00:11:48.120 line:80%
When I asked if you pushed Hutou just now,

00:11:48.920 --> 00:11:51.450 line:80%
why did you nod first
and then shake your head?

00:11:53.640 --> 00:11:55.400 line:80%
I did push him.

00:11:55.670 --> 00:11:57.920 line:80%
But he was too fat.

00:11:58.240 --> 00:12:00.040 line:80%
I couldn't move him.

00:12:00.670 --> 00:12:02.240 line:80%
He chased me,

00:12:02.240 --> 00:12:05.050 line:80%
fell down the stairs himself,

00:12:05.430 --> 00:12:07.620 line:80%
and broke his front teeth.

00:12:07.650 --> 00:12:08.920 line:80%
Hutou said you pushed him!

00:12:08.920 --> 00:12:09.670 line:80%
Shut up!

00:12:09.670 --> 00:12:12.230 line:80%
I knew Hutou fell on his own.

00:12:14.470 --> 00:12:15.640 line:80%
Why did you push him?

00:12:17.120 --> 00:12:18.950 line:80%
He pulled my hair,

00:12:19.660 --> 00:12:21.790 line:80%
snatched my candy,

00:12:22.390 --> 00:12:25.030 line:80%
threw rice water on me,

00:12:25.150 --> 00:12:28.180 line:80%
and called me a jinx's sister,

00:12:29.040 --> 00:12:32.170 line:80%
saying I needed a splash of water
to get rid of my bad luck.

00:12:35.880 --> 00:12:38.580 line:80%
You filthy old hag who deserves
to be buried with no coffin!

00:12:38.580 --> 00:12:40.040 line:80%
Not only do you have a wicked tongue,

00:12:40.040 --> 00:12:41.900 line:80%
you don't even do good deeds
for your grandson.

00:12:41.900 --> 00:12:43.550 line:80%
Aren't you afraid the King of Hell

00:12:43.550 --> 00:12:44.740 line:80%
will rip your tongue out after you die?

00:12:44.740 --> 00:12:46.350 line:80%
How am I wicked?

00:12:46.530 --> 00:12:48.320 line:80%
Did I kill her parents?

00:12:48.580 --> 00:12:51.600 line:80%
Did I kill all those people
who died in her family?

00:12:53.040 --> 00:12:55.000 line:80%
Everyone in Lin'an knows

00:12:55.040 --> 00:12:56.820 line:80%
she's a jinx!

00:12:57.280 --> 00:12:58.950 line:80%
Only you and your husband,

00:12:58.950 --> 00:13:00.590 line:80%
who have no one to bury you when you die,

00:13:00.590 --> 00:13:02.780 line:80%
took in this whole cursed family.

00:13:02.880 --> 00:13:04.120 line:80%
Maybe one day,

00:13:04.120 --> 00:13:06.050 line:80%
she'll bring you to your death too.

00:13:08.280 --> 00:13:09.470 line:80%
If you ask me,

00:13:09.470 --> 00:13:10.640 line:80%
the Fan family

00:13:10.640 --> 00:13:12.710 line:80%
should've gotten out
of Xigu Lane long ago.

00:13:12.710 --> 00:13:15.310 line:80%
Who knows when their enemies
will come looking for them.

00:13:15.310 --> 00:13:18.000 line:80%
-Why are you so mean?
-If I'm going to jinx anyone to death,

00:13:18.000 --> 00:13:20.000 line:80%
you'll be the first one, you old hag.

00:13:20.640 --> 00:13:22.470 line:80%
Why should I leave Xigu Lane?

00:13:23.240 --> 00:13:25.350 line:80%
If you're so scared, you leave.

00:13:26.520 --> 00:13:27.180 line:80%
And listen—

00:13:30.520 --> 00:13:31.470 line:80%
if you ever

00:13:31.980 --> 00:13:34.620 line:80%
lay a finger on Fan Changning again,

00:13:34.640 --> 00:13:36.840 line:80%
whichever hand you use, I'll cut it off.

00:13:37.920 --> 00:13:39.750 line:80%
You think I'm scared of you?

00:13:40.880 --> 00:13:42.160 line:80%
Don't try to scare me.

00:13:43.290 --> 00:13:44.340 line:80%
Scare you?

00:13:47.040 --> 00:13:49.900 line:80%
I can chop a pig's trotter
clean off with one stroke.

00:13:50.640 --> 00:13:52.370 line:80%
Your hand would be even easier.

00:13:53.070 --> 00:13:54.040 line:80%
Left or right?

00:13:54.310 --> 00:13:55.910 line:80%
Which one do you want to keep?

00:13:55.920 --> 00:13:57.520 line:80%
-How about neither?
-Don't!

00:13:58.400 --> 00:13:59.120 line:80%
Hutou!

00:14:00.520 --> 00:14:01.040 line:80%
Hu...

00:14:02.160 --> 00:14:02.760 line:80%
Grandma!

00:14:03.120 --> 00:14:04.190 line:80%
Karma!

00:14:05.000 --> 00:14:06.270 line:80%
This is instant karma!

00:14:06.430 --> 00:14:07.880 line:80%
You saw that, right?

00:14:07.880 --> 00:14:09.350 line:80%
Changyu and I didn't touch this old woman.

00:14:09.350 --> 00:14:10.880 line:80%
She fell on her own.

00:14:11.620 --> 00:14:15.180 line:80%
It was her! She kicked me!

00:14:16.830 --> 00:14:17.570 line:80%
Granny Kang,

00:14:17.600 --> 00:14:19.320 line:80%
we were all watching.

00:14:19.430 --> 00:14:20.660 line:80%
You fell on your own.

00:14:20.680 --> 00:14:22.640 line:80%
You must have been too vicious
with your words,

00:14:22.640 --> 00:14:24.000 line:80%
so heaven punished you.

00:14:24.590 --> 00:14:25.310 line:80%
Exactly.

00:14:25.880 --> 00:14:28.610 line:80%
It was this jinx! She jinxed me!

00:14:28.640 --> 00:14:30.950 line:80%
Get lost! Or I'll jinx you to death!

00:14:30.990 --> 00:14:31.910 line:80%
Granny Kang,

00:14:31.910 --> 00:14:32.830 line:80%
be careful.

00:14:32.830 --> 00:14:34.520 line:80%
Or you may knock your teeth out.

00:14:34.520 --> 00:14:36.680 line:80%
Don't blame Changyu for that too.

00:14:42.160 --> 00:14:42.830 line:80%
Changning.

00:14:44.350 --> 00:14:46.770 line:80%
in the future,
if anyone bullies you outside,

00:14:46.770 --> 00:14:48.500 line:80%
come back and tell me, alright?

00:15:18.240 --> 00:15:19.460 line:80%
How about you...

00:15:19.950 --> 00:15:21.350 line:80%
not wait for the New Year?

00:15:22.200 --> 00:15:23.420 line:80%
Just go now.

00:15:26.650 --> 00:15:28.850 line:80%
Just because of a few words from others,

00:15:29.670 --> 00:15:31.070 line:80%
you want to chase me away?

00:15:33.800 --> 00:15:35.080 line:80%
My family's troubles

00:15:35.880 --> 00:15:38.020 line:80%
have already dragged you in twice.

00:15:40.710 --> 00:15:42.640 line:80%
You don't owe me anything anymore.

00:15:43.590 --> 00:15:46.040 line:80%
If you cut ties with us sooner,

00:15:47.310 --> 00:15:48.400 line:80%
you'll be safer.

00:15:56.640 --> 00:15:58.440 line:80%
You believe that woman's words?

00:16:03.670 --> 00:16:04.310 line:80%
No.

00:16:07.240 --> 00:16:08.570 line:80%
I don't believe in fate,

00:16:09.550 --> 00:16:11.620 line:80%
nor in that nonsense
about being a cursed star

00:16:11.620 --> 00:16:13.190 line:80%
who brings misfortune.

00:16:14.070 --> 00:16:15.550 line:80%
I just think that those people

00:16:15.550 --> 00:16:17.210 line:80%
won't let my family go easily,

00:16:19.760 --> 00:16:21.890 line:80%
so I don't want to drag you down with us.

00:16:22.200 --> 00:16:23.930 line:80%
If you think you can push me away

00:16:24.920 --> 00:16:26.780 line:80%
just because it's for my own good,

00:16:28.310 --> 00:16:29.840 line:80%
then what about Changning?

00:16:30.570 --> 00:16:32.630 line:80%
Are you going to cut ties with her too?

00:16:35.410 --> 00:16:36.060 line:80%
I can't.

00:16:37.070 --> 00:16:38.040 line:80%
She's too young.

00:16:38.900 --> 00:16:40.300 line:80%
I have to keep her with me.

00:16:44.470 --> 00:16:45.280 line:80%
So,

00:16:46.070 --> 00:16:48.270 line:80%
you're only driving me away, is that it?

00:16:55.550 --> 00:16:58.210 line:80%
You're not the type
to take an insult lying down.

00:16:58.880 --> 00:17:00.470 line:80%
If someone splashes water on you,

00:17:00.470 --> 00:17:03.000 line:80%
just teach them a lesson
right then and there.

00:17:05.960 --> 00:17:08.360 line:80%
There's a saying
I once heard from Mr. Wang:

00:17:08.690 --> 00:17:10.750 line:80%
"The law does not punish the masses."

00:17:11.520 --> 00:17:14.520 line:80%
It means that if a large group of people
breaks the law,

00:17:14.899 --> 00:17:17.560 line:80%
the authorities
usually won't punish them all.

00:17:18.149 --> 00:17:20.240 line:80%
Now the whole town is gossiping about me

00:17:20.240 --> 00:17:21.540 line:80%
behind my back.

00:17:22.200 --> 00:17:24.000 line:80%
I might be able to deal with one of them,

00:17:24.000 --> 00:17:25.530 line:80%
but can I deal with them all?

00:17:28.169 --> 00:17:29.900 line:80%
[Young Xie Zheng]

00:17:34.520 --> 00:17:38.850 line:80%
[Young Wei Xuan]

00:17:41.040 --> 00:17:42.790 line:80%
Then have you ever heard of the saying

00:17:42.790 --> 00:17:44.450 line:80%
"make an example of someone"?

00:17:44.870 --> 00:17:46.070 line:80%
Human nature is evil.

00:17:46.440 --> 00:17:48.240 line:80%
If you're weak and easy to bully,

00:17:48.430 --> 00:17:49.890 line:80%
no matter how kind you are,

00:17:50.530 --> 00:17:51.970 line:80%
no one will help you.

00:17:53.880 --> 00:17:55.640 line:80%
But if you rise to power,

00:17:56.630 --> 00:17:58.480 line:80%
even if you've done terrible things,

00:17:58.480 --> 00:18:00.810 line:80%
plenty of people will rush to flatter you.

00:18:03.150 --> 00:18:06.140 line:80%
Superstitions
are just meant to confuse people.

00:18:08.210 --> 00:18:10.670 line:80%
Like the candy
that hit Granny Kang just now—

00:18:11.420 --> 00:18:12.440 line:80%
in her eyes,

00:18:13.640 --> 00:18:15.570 line:80%
it was just a ghost playing tricks.

00:18:17.420 --> 00:18:19.120 line:80%
You can say these things to me,

00:18:20.150 --> 00:18:21.480 line:80%
but if you start distancing yourself

00:18:21.480 --> 00:18:23.740 line:80%
from Mr. Zhao and Mrs. Zhao because of it,

00:18:24.350 --> 00:18:25.810 line:80%
they will be heartbroken.

00:18:31.190 --> 00:18:32.790 line:80%
Then take what I said earlier

00:18:33.150 --> 00:18:34.550 line:80%
as a moment of impulse.

00:18:35.960 --> 00:18:37.040 line:80%
Please stay.

00:18:39.150 --> 00:18:40.550 line:80%
So it's up to you

00:18:41.200 --> 00:18:42.800 line:80%
whether I leave or stay, huh?

00:18:43.510 --> 00:18:44.770 line:80%
You've got some nerve.

00:18:47.680 --> 00:18:49.200 line:80%
Don't be mad.

00:18:49.870 --> 00:18:52.330 line:80%
The candy I bought you
wasn't meant for that.

00:18:52.830 --> 00:18:55.000 line:80%
You should have gone and found
some pebbles.

00:18:55.000 --> 00:18:56.440 line:80%
Candy is expensive.

00:18:55.250 --> 00:18:57.450 line:80%
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

00:18:56.800 --> 00:18:57.860 line:80%
It was not worth it.

00:18:58.520 --> 00:18:59.720 line:80%
♪ With very pale colors ♪

00:19:00.520 --> 00:19:03.480 line:80%
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

00:19:03.940 --> 00:19:06.430 line:80%
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

00:19:07.180 --> 00:19:08.660 line:80%
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

00:19:07.720 --> 00:19:09.340 line:80%
I never had the chance to ask before.

00:19:09.340 --> 00:19:13.500 line:80%
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

00:19:10.520 --> 00:19:13.450 line:80%
Why did you become an armed escort
and risk your life?

00:19:15.360 --> 00:19:16.360 line:80%
Because...

00:19:16.950 --> 00:19:19.420 line:80%
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

00:19:17.260 --> 00:19:19.120 line:80%
there are things I simply must do.

00:19:20.040 --> 00:19:21.070 line:80%
Just like how

00:19:20.220 --> 00:19:21.830 line:80%
♪ The light shines ♪

00:19:21.090 --> 00:19:23.390 line:80%
you want to keep running
your father's butcher shop.

00:19:22.520 --> 00:19:25.260 line:80%
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

00:19:25.000 --> 00:19:25.870 line:80%
My father

00:19:25.710 --> 00:19:28.320 line:80%
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

00:19:27.340 --> 00:19:28.940 line:80%
also had unfinished business.

00:19:28.940 --> 00:19:30.680 line:80%
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

00:19:30.440 --> 00:19:31.870 line:80%
I want to finish it for him.

00:19:31.130 --> 00:19:36.010 line:80%
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

00:19:35.760 --> 00:19:37.760 line:80%
So your family ran an escort agency?

00:19:38.480 --> 00:19:40.200 line:80%
And you were the Young Master?

00:19:38.540 --> 00:19:39.610 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love ♪

00:19:39.640 --> 00:19:42.330 line:80%
♪ Will never end ♪

00:19:41.440 --> 00:19:43.760 line:80%
Rebuilding an escort agency
costs a lot of money.

00:19:43.000 --> 00:19:43.880 line:80%
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

00:19:43.900 --> 00:19:46.280 line:80%
♪ For a lifetime ♪

00:19:44.720 --> 00:19:46.350 line:80%
When I have some money to spare,

00:19:46.350 --> 00:19:47.780 line:80%
I can help you out.

00:19:46.910 --> 00:19:50.950 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:19:48.200 --> 00:19:49.150 line:80%
No need.

00:19:50.000 --> 00:19:51.310 line:80%
I haven't repaid you

00:19:51.310 --> 00:19:52.480 line:80%
for saving my life yet.

00:19:51.470 --> 00:19:54.970 line:80%
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

00:19:54.000 --> 00:19:55.850 line:80%
That's a completely different matter.

00:19:55.850 --> 00:19:56.780 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love
will not be like sand ♪

00:19:56.310 --> 00:19:58.100 line:80%
When you agreed to marry into my family,

00:19:56.800 --> 00:19:59.310 line:80%
♪ Slipping into the sea ♪

00:19:58.630 --> 00:20:00.000 line:80%
we were already even.

00:20:00.590 --> 00:20:01.530 line:80%
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

00:20:01.550 --> 00:20:03.900 line:80%
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

00:20:01.720 --> 00:20:03.180 line:80%
You want to be even with me?

00:20:04.700 --> 00:20:08.590 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:20:06.900 --> 00:20:08.390 line:80%
That's not what I meant.

00:20:09.070 --> 00:20:17.260 line:80%
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

00:20:20.070 --> 00:20:21.760 line:80%
We've known each other for so long,

00:20:21.760 --> 00:20:24.220 line:80%
yet I still don't know
when your birthday is.

00:20:24.960 --> 00:20:26.680 line:80%
My birthday is easy to remember.

00:20:26.680 --> 00:20:28.200 line:80%
It's 2 days after the Lantern Festival.

00:20:28.200 --> 00:20:29.910 line:80%
The holiday spirit is still strong then.

00:20:29.910 --> 00:20:30.910 line:80%
It's very lively.

00:20:31.760 --> 00:20:32.690 line:80%
What do you want?

00:20:35.720 --> 00:20:38.720 line:80%
I want my family all together,

00:20:38.720 --> 00:20:39.630 line:80%
safe and sound.

00:20:40.520 --> 00:20:41.480 line:80%
And if in the spring,

00:20:41.480 --> 00:20:45.140 line:80%
I could keep another litter of piglets,
that would be even better.

00:20:52.000 --> 00:20:56.060 line:80%
[Capital]

00:20:55.130 --> 00:20:57.740 line:80%
Your Majesty, I have a proposal.

00:20:58.280 --> 00:20:59.910 line:80%
Grand Tutor, please go ahead.

00:20:59.910 --> 00:21:00.720 line:80%
Your Majesty,

00:21:01.070 --> 00:21:03.150 line:80%
the weather has been erratic this year.

00:21:03.150 --> 00:21:05.680 line:80%
The land is barren,
and the crops have failed.

00:21:06.070 --> 00:21:07.870 line:80%
In this year of disaster,

00:21:08.310 --> 00:21:10.880 line:80%
if we still transport grain
to the front line,

00:21:11.150 --> 00:21:13.070 line:80%
I fear it will cause a refugee crisis

00:21:13.070 --> 00:21:15.200 line:80%
and shake the foundation of the state.

00:21:16.000 --> 00:21:18.390 line:80%
Your Majesty, I implore you

00:21:18.590 --> 00:21:21.200 line:80%
to revoke the restoration order
for the front line.

00:21:21.200 --> 00:21:23.710 line:80%
I humbly ask for Your Majesty's judgment.

00:21:24.200 --> 00:21:27.420 line:80%
The situation on the front line
changes rapidly.

00:21:27.800 --> 00:21:30.910 line:80%
Even the Marquis of Wu'an
has fallen in battle.

00:21:31.950 --> 00:21:35.480 line:80%
Provisions before a great battle
are of the utmost importance.

00:21:35.870 --> 00:21:37.760 line:80%
How can we easily revoke the order?

00:21:37.760 --> 00:21:39.630 line:80%
After years of war,

00:21:39.630 --> 00:21:42.590 line:80%
the treasury is now empty
and cannot bear the burden.

00:21:43.550 --> 00:21:46.150 line:80%
If the treasury is empty,
levy grain locally

00:21:46.150 --> 00:21:47.870 line:80%
to solve the urgent need.

00:21:48.150 --> 00:21:50.100 line:80%
After we pacify Chongzhou,

00:21:50.240 --> 00:21:52.760 line:80%
we can return it to the people.

00:21:53.060 --> 00:21:55.720 line:80%
It is deep winter now,
and the end of the year is approaching.

00:21:55.720 --> 00:21:58.490 line:80%
The people's surplus grain is not enough
to fill their own stomachs.

00:21:58.490 --> 00:21:59.960 line:80%
Levying grain locally?

00:22:00.280 --> 00:22:01.410 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei,

00:22:01.720 --> 00:22:03.360 line:80%
are you not worried

00:22:03.830 --> 00:22:05.890 line:80%
that it will incite a civil uprising?

00:22:06.150 --> 00:22:08.240 line:80%
The front line is engulfed
in flames of war,

00:22:08.240 --> 00:22:10.480 line:80%
and our soldiers
are fighting bloody battles.

00:22:10.480 --> 00:22:12.740 line:80%
Provisions are the lifeline of the army.

00:22:12.800 --> 00:22:14.660 line:80%
How can they go a day without them?

00:22:15.040 --> 00:22:18.760 line:80%
If the enemy takes this chance
to march south and breach our cities,

00:22:18.760 --> 00:22:22.470 line:80%
I fear it will bring disaster
and ruin to our nation.

00:22:22.800 --> 00:22:23.760 line:80%
Grand Tutor,

00:22:24.310 --> 00:22:28.310 line:80%
do you dare to bear
such a heavy responsibility alone?

00:22:29.110 --> 00:22:30.800 line:80%
Surely, Grand Tutor Li,

00:22:30.800 --> 00:22:33.150 line:80%
you do not wish to repeat the tragedy
of 16 years ago,

00:22:33.150 --> 00:22:35.760 line:80%
when provisions
failed to reach Jinzhou City,

00:22:35.760 --> 00:22:38.490 line:80%
leading to its massacre?

00:22:51.010 --> 00:22:52.730 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei is farsighted.

00:22:52.730 --> 00:22:55.500 line:80%
He is truly the most loyal subject
of Great Yin.

00:22:55.570 --> 00:22:59.420 line:80%
[Diligent and Virtuous]

00:22:55.910 --> 00:22:58.310 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei is loyal and righteous.

00:22:59.480 --> 00:23:03.460 line:80%
[Wei Residence]

00:23:14.220 --> 00:23:14.900 line:80%
Uncle,

00:23:15.280 --> 00:23:17.300 line:80%
when I grow up,
I want to be like my father,

00:23:17.300 --> 00:23:18.960 line:80%
fighting on the battlefield.

00:23:33.150 --> 00:23:35.270 line:80%
[Mrs. Wei]

00:23:34.760 --> 00:23:35.690 line:80%
Prime Minister.

00:23:37.760 --> 00:23:38.440 line:80%
Come in.

00:23:47.520 --> 00:23:50.120 line:80%
Prime Minister,
please have some ginseng tea.

00:23:54.690 --> 00:23:56.220 line:80%
Have Zheng's remains

00:23:56.390 --> 00:23:58.040 line:80%
still not been found?

00:24:02.280 --> 00:24:05.250 line:80%
This child is of the Wei family's
bloodline.

00:24:05.280 --> 00:24:09.650 line:80%
And he was raised with such care by you.

00:24:10.040 --> 00:24:12.770 line:80%
They say a maternal uncle
is like a second father.

00:24:12.830 --> 00:24:15.750 line:80%
It's such a pity that he died like this.

00:24:16.200 --> 00:24:18.870 line:80%
Please take care of yourself,
Prime Minister.

00:24:22.390 --> 00:24:24.480 line:80%
-And Xuan...
-Please go back.

00:24:27.800 --> 00:24:29.520 line:80%
I spoke out of turn.

00:24:30.350 --> 00:24:32.610 line:80%
I beg your forgiveness, Prime Minister.

00:24:37.470 --> 00:24:38.870 line:80%
I shall take my leave.

00:25:07.630 --> 00:25:08.480 line:80%
Prime Minister,

00:25:08.480 --> 00:25:10.110 line:80%
He Jingyuan, Governor of Jizhou,

00:25:10.110 --> 00:25:12.110 line:80%
has sent a brocade box by fast horse.

00:25:13.250 --> 00:25:18.040 line:80%
[To Prime Minister Wei of Great Yin]

00:25:22.070 --> 00:25:24.380 line:80%
He has always been cautious.

00:25:27.040 --> 00:25:30.950 line:80%
[To Wei Qilin]

00:25:28.070 --> 00:25:29.130 line:80%
To General Suituo,

00:25:29.870 --> 00:25:31.280 line:80%
Jinzhou is in critical danger.

00:25:31.280 --> 00:25:33.000 line:80%
I must return to the capital
for an urgent matter.

00:25:33.000 --> 00:25:34.870 line:80%
Therefore, I am sending
my household general, Wei Qilin,

00:25:34.870 --> 00:25:38.180 line:80%
to request immediate reinforcements
with the Tiger Tally

00:25:38.390 --> 00:25:39.550 line:80%
to resist Beijue together

00:25:39.550 --> 00:25:41.490 line:80%
and save Crown Prince Chengde.

00:25:41.830 --> 00:25:43.550 line:80%
General, Wei Yan.

00:25:44.070 --> 00:25:47.130 line:80%
Eighth day of the fifth month,
the 26th year of Taikang.

00:25:53.280 --> 00:25:55.590 line:80%
It seems He Jingyuan

00:25:55.590 --> 00:25:58.400 line:80%
is using his own life as leverage

00:25:58.520 --> 00:26:02.480 line:80%
to make me spare the two daughters
of that traitor.

00:26:03.000 --> 00:26:04.380 line:80%
He Jingyuan is so bold.

00:26:04.760 --> 00:26:07.260 line:80%
Prime Minister, you shouldn't have been
soft-hearted back then

00:26:07.260 --> 00:26:09.720 line:80%
and stopped searching
for Wei Qilin's body.

00:26:12.310 --> 00:26:13.310 line:80%
Zheng's

00:26:13.800 --> 00:26:16.530 line:80%
sudden investigation
into the Jinzhou massacre

00:26:17.240 --> 00:26:20.070 line:80%
must have been instigated
by someone with ulterior motives.

00:26:20.070 --> 00:26:21.280 line:80%
Now,

00:26:21.350 --> 00:26:23.830 line:80%
even He Jingyuan goes against my orders.

00:26:24.000 --> 00:26:25.060 line:80%
Why don't you let me

00:26:25.200 --> 00:26:26.800 line:80%
go and get rid of He Jingyuan?

00:26:29.550 --> 00:26:32.110 line:80%
The battle in Chongzhou
is critical right now.

00:26:32.110 --> 00:26:34.960 line:80%
If I lose a weapon like He Jingyuan,

00:26:35.060 --> 00:26:36.990 line:80%
the Northwest will be in peril.

00:26:38.280 --> 00:26:38.800 line:80%
I see.

00:26:38.960 --> 00:26:39.830 line:80%
Forget it.

00:26:39.870 --> 00:26:41.480 line:80%
They are just two girls.

00:26:41.860 --> 00:26:45.920 line:80%
[To Wei Qilin]

00:26:42.480 --> 00:26:43.280 line:80%
Let them live.

00:26:43.910 --> 00:26:46.240 line:80%
How much trouble can they possibly cause?

00:27:05.760 --> 00:27:06.760 line:80%
Lord Li?

00:27:08.970 --> 00:27:15.420 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:27:09.240 --> 00:27:11.000 line:80%
Your husband is not home today?

00:27:12.310 --> 00:27:13.640 line:80%
He went out on business.

00:27:14.390 --> 00:27:16.520 line:80%
Do you need him for something, My Lord?

00:27:16.800 --> 00:27:18.060 line:80%
Just asking casually.

00:27:18.310 --> 00:27:18.960 line:80%
By the way,

00:27:20.200 --> 00:27:21.550 line:80%
regarding the case involving your family,

00:27:21.550 --> 00:27:23.280 line:80%
I have figured out everything.

00:27:23.570 --> 00:27:24.570 line:80%
Who did it?

00:27:25.310 --> 00:27:27.800 line:80%
The Qingzhou Government Office
found that the attacks on your family

00:27:27.800 --> 00:27:31.240 line:80%
stemmed from an escort mission
your father undertook years ago.

00:27:31.240 --> 00:27:32.520 line:80%
Rumor has it that it involved
a treasure map

00:27:32.520 --> 00:27:34.800 line:80%
left by
the previous dynasty's royal family.

00:27:34.800 --> 00:27:35.960 line:80%
Over a decade ago,

00:27:36.200 --> 00:27:38.530 line:80%
everyone in the escort agency was killed.

00:27:38.630 --> 00:27:40.390 line:80%
Only your father survived.

00:27:41.040 --> 00:27:44.370 line:80%
That was why he could settle down here
in Lin'an Town all these years.

00:27:44.370 --> 00:27:46.170 line:80%
After the turmoil in Chongzhou,

00:27:46.390 --> 00:27:48.520 line:80%
the treasure map was brought up again.

00:27:48.650 --> 00:27:51.550 line:80%
The bandits from Qingfeng Stronghold
tracked down your father,

00:27:51.550 --> 00:27:54.280 line:80%
which is why
they repeatedly attacked your home—

00:27:54.950 --> 00:27:57.590 line:80%
to get that treasure map.

00:27:58.000 --> 00:27:59.320 line:80%
Treasure map?

00:28:01.480 --> 00:28:03.680 line:80%
I've never heard my parents mention it.

00:28:04.440 --> 00:28:04.960 line:80%
Yes.

00:28:06.480 --> 00:28:08.680 line:80%
So, rumors can be deadly.

00:28:11.720 --> 00:28:13.910 line:80%
Why did Li Huaian make up such a lie

00:28:13.910 --> 00:28:15.170 line:80%
just to close the case?

00:28:19.150 --> 00:28:20.040 line:80%
My parents...

00:28:21.440 --> 00:28:23.390 line:80%
died just because of a rumor?

00:28:26.680 --> 00:28:29.970 line:80%
A few days ago,
the rebels in Chongzhou announced

00:28:30.470 --> 00:28:32.910 line:80%
that they had already found
the treasure map.

00:28:32.910 --> 00:28:35.040 line:80%
The Qingfeng Stronghold bandits
won't come to town anymore.

00:28:35.040 --> 00:28:36.240 line:80%
You can rest assured.

00:28:38.730 --> 00:28:41.470 line:80%
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

00:28:43.280 --> 00:28:45.610 line:80%
If there's a chance to catch those bandits

00:28:46.630 --> 00:28:48.430 line:80%
and let my parents rest in peace,

00:28:48.470 --> 00:28:50.070 line:80%
I am at your command, My Lord.

00:28:54.790 --> 00:29:02.220 line:80%
[Fill Your Belly]

00:28:57.400 --> 00:28:58.450 line:80%
This is the relief fund sent

00:28:58.450 --> 00:29:00.180 line:80%
by Governor He of Jizhou, out of

00:29:00.390 --> 00:29:03.990 line:80%
concern for the people.
He specially appointed me to deliver it.

00:29:08.440 --> 00:29:09.390 line:80%
Is it all for me?

00:29:10.320 --> 00:29:12.800 line:80%
For those who suffered at the hands
of the Qingfeng Stronghold bandits

00:29:12.800 --> 00:29:14.110 line:80%
and lost family members,

00:29:14.110 --> 00:29:15.910 line:80%
the government has issued
consolation money.

00:29:15.910 --> 00:29:17.370 line:80%
It's not just your family.

00:29:17.830 --> 00:29:19.390 line:80%
The standard is 10 taels per person.

00:29:19.390 --> 00:29:20.850 line:80%
Here is 30 taels of silver.

00:29:21.520 --> 00:29:22.520 line:80%
Please accept it.

00:29:31.000 --> 00:29:33.150 line:80%
Dry weather!

00:29:33.800 --> 00:29:36.280 line:80%
Beware of fire!

00:29:40.550 --> 00:29:41.630 line:80%
It's flying over!

00:29:43.070 --> 00:29:44.220 line:80%
Changyu,

00:29:44.310 --> 00:29:46.200 line:80%
you talked in your sleep again last night.

00:29:46.200 --> 00:29:47.070 line:80%
What did I say?

00:29:48.590 --> 00:29:52.310 line:80%
You said you were afraid the spices
from out of town weren't authentic.

00:29:52.310 --> 00:29:53.390 line:80%
You said,

00:29:53.390 --> 00:29:55.720 line:80%
"Five spices aren't enough, we need six."

00:29:56.000 --> 00:29:58.740 line:80%
Then you said that if Zheng left,

00:29:58.760 --> 00:30:02.400 line:80%
you'd never find
such a handsome husband again.

00:30:07.040 --> 00:30:08.350 line:80%
Keep your voice down.

00:30:11.070 --> 00:30:12.000 line:80%
Changyu,

00:30:12.000 --> 00:30:13.930 line:80%
we don't have to move anymore?

00:30:17.630 --> 00:30:20.680 line:80%
But I already told the others
in the village

00:30:20.680 --> 00:30:21.810 line:80%
that we were moving.

00:30:22.000 --> 00:30:24.200 line:80%
It's so embarrassing not to move now.

00:30:25.110 --> 00:30:27.040 line:80%
Can we move out for a little while,

00:30:27.040 --> 00:30:27.970 line:80%
then move back?

00:30:28.000 --> 00:30:29.530 line:80%
That would count as moving.

00:30:31.350 --> 00:30:32.830 line:80%
Why are you so smart?

00:30:34.150 --> 00:30:35.000 line:80%
How about this?

00:30:35.000 --> 00:30:36.040 line:80%
Tell them

00:30:36.040 --> 00:30:37.440 line:80%
we don't have to move anymore,

00:30:37.440 --> 00:30:38.860 line:80%
and give them some candy.

00:30:39.040 --> 00:30:40.670 line:80%
Then they won't laugh at you.

00:30:41.000 --> 00:30:41.870 line:80%
Changyu,

00:30:41.870 --> 00:30:44.480 line:80%
when will you go back to sleep with Zheng?

00:30:44.630 --> 00:30:46.490 line:80%
You're squeezing into my small bed
every day.

00:30:46.490 --> 00:30:48.350 line:80%
It's hard for me to even turn over.

00:30:48.870 --> 00:30:49.830 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao says

00:30:49.830 --> 00:30:52.960 line:80%
that a husband and wife
should sleep together for life.

00:30:54.630 --> 00:30:55.150 line:80%
What?

00:30:55.440 --> 00:30:57.230 line:80%
Are you sick of me already?

00:30:57.350 --> 00:30:58.140 line:80%
I don't care.

00:30:58.280 --> 00:30:59.610 line:80%
I want to sleep with you.

00:30:59.800 --> 00:31:01.220 line:80%
For a lifetime!

00:31:02.310 --> 00:31:03.480 line:80%
How dare you be sick of me!

00:31:03.480 --> 00:31:04.400 line:80%
Take that!

00:31:04.680 --> 00:31:05.650 line:80%
Are you still sick of me?

00:31:05.650 --> 00:31:07.240 line:80%
-No!
-Are you?

00:31:07.670 --> 00:31:09.150 line:80%
-No!
-Are you?

00:31:09.630 --> 00:31:10.760 line:80%
You're not, are you?

00:31:10.910 --> 00:31:12.020 line:80%
I yield.

00:31:13.070 --> 00:31:14.120 line:80%
Beg for mercy, quickly!

00:31:14.120 --> 00:31:14.980 line:80%
Changyu!

00:31:36.630 --> 00:31:37.630 line:80%
All you do is eat.

00:31:38.520 --> 00:31:39.260 line:80%
You're getting so fat.

00:31:39.260 --> 00:31:40.860 line:80%
I wonder if you can still fly.

00:31:50.200 --> 00:31:50.760 line:80%
Go now.

00:32:00.830 --> 00:32:03.850 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:32:03.870 --> 00:32:04.870 line:80%
Let's go.

00:32:05.660 --> 00:32:06.400 line:80%
Let's go!

00:32:18.550 --> 00:32:19.610 line:80%
Morning, Mrs. Fan.

00:32:20.830 --> 00:32:21.760 line:80%
Morning.

00:32:29.590 --> 00:32:30.870 line:80%
Lord Li?

00:32:31.630 --> 00:32:33.360 line:80%
Why are you at the Song's house?

00:32:34.320 --> 00:32:39.430 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:32:34.960 --> 00:32:37.440 line:80%
I rented a vacant house from a broker.

00:32:37.440 --> 00:32:40.370 line:80%
When I got here,
I realized it was opposite your home.

00:32:41.440 --> 00:32:43.040 line:80%
So this family is named Song?

00:32:44.390 --> 00:32:46.120 line:80%
Aren't you going back to Jizhou?

00:32:46.120 --> 00:32:47.280 line:80%
I promised I would find

00:32:47.280 --> 00:32:48.940 line:80%
the murderer of your parents.

00:32:48.960 --> 00:32:50.020 line:80%
I must keep my word.

00:32:58.680 --> 00:32:59.630 line:80%
Lord Li?

00:33:04.350 --> 00:33:06.110 line:80%
To catch the murderer, Lord Li

00:33:06.130 --> 00:33:07.660 line:80%
decided to stay for a while.

00:33:07.720 --> 00:33:09.720 line:80%
And he even rented Song Yan's house.

00:33:10.070 --> 00:33:11.530 line:80%
Isn't that a coincidence?

00:33:12.730 --> 00:33:14.260 line:80%
What a coincidence indeed.

00:33:17.280 --> 00:33:18.610 line:80%
I won't disturb you two.

00:33:31.760 --> 00:33:32.560 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:33:32.630 --> 00:33:35.100 line:80%
The falcon is gone.

00:33:38.390 --> 00:33:40.590 line:80%
Maybe the lid
wasn't closed tightly last night.

00:33:40.590 --> 00:33:43.800 line:80%
After its wings healed,
it flew away on its own.

00:33:44.310 --> 00:33:46.420 line:80%
This falcon has parents of its own.

00:33:46.590 --> 00:33:48.540 line:80%
It needs to go home to find them.

00:33:49.070 --> 00:33:49.830 line:80%
Don't cry.

00:33:51.590 --> 00:33:53.060 line:80%
There's nothing we can do.

00:33:53.240 --> 00:33:55.370 line:80%
The falcon has a family too.

00:33:56.070 --> 00:33:57.520 line:80%
Don't cry.

00:33:59.040 --> 00:34:00.280 line:80%
It will fly back.

00:34:04.550 --> 00:34:07.760 line:80%
Can you pinky-promise me for the falcon?

00:34:18.120 --> 00:34:20.249 line:80%
You're going to leave sooner or later,

00:34:21.470 --> 00:34:22.160 line:80%
aren't you?

00:34:24.160 --> 00:34:25.640 line:80%
In my current situation,

00:34:26.430 --> 00:34:27.810 line:80%
loving someone

00:34:28.510 --> 00:34:29.910 line:80%
only puts them in danger.

00:34:35.240 --> 00:34:36.160 line:80%
People

00:34:36.870 --> 00:34:39.650 line:80%
are not deities
who cut off emotions and desires.

00:34:40.990 --> 00:34:42.160 line:80%
It's hard to control

00:34:43.350 --> 00:34:44.430 line:80%
your feelings.

00:34:51.080 --> 00:34:52.310 line:80%
Don't coax her.

00:34:53.160 --> 00:34:54.890 line:80%
Changning is just a bit lonely.

00:34:55.120 --> 00:34:57.240 line:80%
I'll buy a cage of chicks in the spring.

00:34:57.240 --> 00:34:59.840 line:80%
With new playmates,
she'll forget the falcon.

00:35:00.720 --> 00:35:01.720 line:80%
In the spring,

00:35:01.720 --> 00:35:04.310 line:80%
I'll buy you a big cage of chicks, okay?

00:35:04.560 --> 00:35:06.640 line:80%
No. I want the falcon.

00:35:11.800 --> 00:35:12.390 line:80%
You don't want that?

00:35:12.390 --> 00:35:13.600 line:80%
I wasn't coaxing her.

00:35:14.720 --> 00:35:15.910 line:80%
To fully tame a falcon,

00:35:15.910 --> 00:35:17.430 line:80%
you have to let it fly first.

00:35:17.430 --> 00:35:18.630 line:80%
Only one that returns

00:35:18.640 --> 00:35:20.160 line:80%
is truly tamed.

00:35:22.950 --> 00:35:25.350 line:80%
But there's no guarantee it
will come back.

00:35:33.780 --> 00:35:37.300 line:80%
[Aspiring to the Clouds]

00:35:35.160 --> 00:35:37.220 line:80%
So you're really not leaving Lin'an?

00:35:37.350 --> 00:35:38.560 line:80%
I was so happy when I heard the news

00:35:38.560 --> 00:35:40.360 line:80%
that I couldn't sleep all night.

00:35:40.390 --> 00:35:41.640 line:80%
I'll show you something.

00:35:41.640 --> 00:35:43.160 line:80%
I've been preparing it for a long time.

00:35:43.160 --> 00:35:44.870 line:80%
-Come on.
-What is it?

00:35:47.720 --> 00:35:48.620 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:35:48.620 --> 00:35:49.220 line:80%
Look.

00:35:52.830 --> 00:35:54.660 line:80%
The auspicious time has arrived!

00:35:54.660 --> 00:35:57.150 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:35:57.620 --> 00:35:59.210 line:80%
[Braised Pork Belly] [Braised Pig's Ear]

00:35:59.250 --> 00:36:00.900 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:36:08.160 --> 00:36:09.460 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:36:13.950 --> 00:36:15.310 line:80%
Bravo!

00:36:16.410 --> 00:36:19.470 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:36:26.910 --> 00:36:27.680 line:80%
Pray to the God of Wealth,

00:36:27.680 --> 00:36:29.410 line:80%
and may your business prosper!

00:36:41.990 --> 00:36:42.790 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:36:44.080 --> 00:36:44.760 line:80%
Nothing.

00:36:45.160 --> 00:36:46.560 line:80%
Let's offer the incense.

00:36:48.540 --> 00:36:52.750 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:36:49.030 --> 00:36:51.760 line:80%
Okay.

00:36:58.910 --> 00:37:00.120 line:80%
What would you like to eat?

00:37:00.120 --> 00:37:01.720 line:80%
Your meat smells delicious.

00:37:01.800 --> 00:37:03.280 line:80%
I want a piece that's not too fatty.

00:37:03.280 --> 00:37:04.760 line:80%
None of them is too fatty.
They're all good.

00:37:04.540 --> 00:37:06.430 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:37:05.120 --> 00:37:05.940 line:80%
Pick a big one.

00:37:06.040 --> 00:37:06.720 line:80%
Okay.

00:37:07.350 --> 00:37:08.550 line:80%
I'll weigh it for you.

00:37:08.990 --> 00:37:09.830 line:80%
Come back often.

00:37:09.830 --> 00:37:10.470 line:80%
Okay.

00:37:10.990 --> 00:37:12.360 line:80%
Changyu?

00:37:12.760 --> 00:37:13.900 line:80%
It's me, it's me.

00:37:14.030 --> 00:37:16.450 line:80%
Your shop has been closed for a while.

00:37:16.560 --> 00:37:18.760 line:80%
We couldn't buy braised meat anywhere.

00:37:19.030 --> 00:37:21.890 line:80%
Turns out you came to Yixiang Restaurant
to make it.

00:37:23.200 --> 00:37:23.990 line:80%
Mrs. Fan

00:37:23.990 --> 00:37:26.120 line:80%
is partnering with Yixiang Restaurant now.

00:37:26.120 --> 00:37:28.430 line:80%
She'll sell exclusively here from now on.

00:37:28.430 --> 00:37:30.800 line:80%
Ma'am, feel free
to come by anytime if you like it.

00:37:30.800 --> 00:37:33.230 line:80%
Changyu's pork used to come

00:37:33.350 --> 00:37:34.910 line:80%
with free offal.

00:37:35.200 --> 00:37:36.720 line:80%
Then I won't be polite.

00:37:36.720 --> 00:37:37.740 line:80%
Look at this.

00:37:37.830 --> 00:37:39.180 line:80%
I... this...

00:37:39.210 --> 00:37:40.240 line:80%
This time...

00:37:40.600 --> 00:37:41.680 line:80%
Well, this time...

00:37:41.680 --> 00:37:43.310 line:80%
Changyu's braised meat

00:37:43.310 --> 00:37:44.580 line:80%
used to be home-style.

00:37:45.240 --> 00:37:47.310 line:80%
Now that she's with Yixiang Restaurant,

00:37:47.310 --> 00:37:50.230 line:80%
the ingredients and recipe are upgraded.

00:37:50.510 --> 00:37:51.900 line:80%
Let alone offal,

00:37:52.080 --> 00:37:55.030 line:80%
even the stock is pricier.

00:37:57.830 --> 00:37:58.830 line:80%
Well,

00:37:59.080 --> 00:38:01.280 line:80%
then how can we common folk afford that?

00:38:02.600 --> 00:38:03.560 line:80%
Forget it.

00:38:03.680 --> 00:38:05.430 line:80%
I'll look elsewhere.

00:38:05.430 --> 00:38:07.030 line:80%
We are opening today,

00:38:07.030 --> 00:38:08.350 line:80%
so we want to start on a lucky note.

00:38:08.350 --> 00:38:09.610 line:80%
If you

00:38:09.870 --> 00:38:11.510 line:80%
can bring us 5 customers in the future,

00:38:11.510 --> 00:38:13.370 line:80%
you'll get a 20 percent discount.

00:38:13.390 --> 00:38:15.190 line:80%
25 percent off for 10 customers.

00:38:15.350 --> 00:38:17.610 line:80%
And 30 percent off for 20. How about that?

00:38:18.430 --> 00:38:19.030 line:80%
Alright.

00:38:20.640 --> 00:38:21.910 line:80%
Changyu,

00:38:21.910 --> 00:38:23.460 line:80%
pick two good pieces of meat for me.

00:38:23.370 --> 00:38:25.580 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:38:23.510 --> 00:38:25.640 line:80%
It's my husband's birthday today.

00:38:25.950 --> 00:38:26.560 line:80%
Okay.

00:38:28.160 --> 00:38:30.560 line:80%
I guarantee it'll be delicious
and generous.

00:38:30.560 --> 00:38:31.310 line:80%
That piece.

00:38:40.430 --> 00:38:41.680 line:80%
I didn't want to offer free offal before,

00:38:41.680 --> 00:38:43.830 line:80%
and the customers
were unwilling to accept it.

00:38:43.830 --> 00:38:44.760 line:80%
You just said a few words,

00:38:44.760 --> 00:38:46.430 line:80%
and they rushed to give us money.

00:38:46.430 --> 00:38:49.160 line:80%
Qianqian,
you're really amazing at doing business.

00:38:49.160 --> 00:38:50.730 line:80%
Undercutting isn't business.

00:38:50.730 --> 00:38:53.260 line:80%
Mutual benefit
is what business is all about.

00:38:59.390 --> 00:39:01.030 line:80%
The great man is he who is in harmony,

00:39:01.030 --> 00:39:03.360 line:80%
in his attributes, with heaven and earth;

00:39:03.560 --> 00:39:05.820 line:80%
in his brightness, with the sun and moon;

00:39:05.830 --> 00:39:08.510 line:80%
in his orderly procedure,
with the four seasons;

00:39:08.510 --> 00:39:09.570 line:80%
and in his relation to
what is fortunate and what is calamitous,

00:39:09.570 --> 00:39:11.100 line:80%
with the spiritual beings.

00:39:11.910 --> 00:39:13.030 line:80%
He naturally—

00:39:32.950 --> 00:39:34.280 line:80%
Your Lordship honors me
with your presence.

00:39:34.280 --> 00:39:35.600 line:80%
My wait was not in vain.

00:39:37.910 --> 00:39:41.040 line:80%
Tell me. What is your purpose
in coming to the Fan family?

00:39:43.830 --> 00:39:45.090 line:80%
I came to the Fan family

00:39:45.510 --> 00:39:47.240 line:80%
only to see you, Your Lordship.

00:39:51.200 --> 00:39:53.460 line:80%
We have known each other since childhood

00:39:53.510 --> 00:39:56.110 line:80%
and both learned martial arts
from General He.

00:39:57.720 --> 00:39:59.910 line:80%
Since the conflict between the Li and Wei,

00:39:59.910 --> 00:40:01.760 line:80%
we've been avoiding each other.

00:40:02.910 --> 00:40:03.760 line:80%
It has been

00:40:04.280 --> 00:40:05.680 line:80%
over a decade, hasn't it?

00:40:08.870 --> 00:40:10.510 line:80%
I am curious now.

00:40:11.080 --> 00:40:12.080 line:80%
Are you a Li

00:40:12.720 --> 00:40:13.760 line:80%
or a Wei?

00:40:45.680 --> 00:40:46.900 line:80%
I only serve Great Yin

00:40:47.830 --> 00:40:48.690 line:80%
and the people.

00:40:51.030 --> 00:40:52.760 line:80%
What about you, Your Lordship?

00:40:53.350 --> 00:40:54.750 line:80%
Which side are you on now?

00:40:55.710 --> 00:40:56.720 line:80%
Anyone can say

00:40:56.950 --> 00:40:57.870 line:80%
pretty words.

00:41:01.950 --> 00:41:03.350 line:80%
I have always

00:41:03.430 --> 00:41:04.560 line:80%
only served myself.

00:41:06.680 --> 00:41:09.230 line:80%
The conflict between Li and Wei
has become chaotic.

00:41:09.230 --> 00:41:12.350 line:80%
And you intend to establish
your own faction in the future.

00:41:12.350 --> 00:41:15.470 line:80%
Do you wish to make this chaos even worse?